About

Hi, I’m Keith Ingersoll. I’m a lead data scientist at Civis Analytics. I work on Creative Focus, a tool that uses surveys and algorithms to pair audiences with the messages they find most persuasive. I’m also a maintainer of the Python and R client libraries for the Civis API. I tweet using the handle @_keithing and I can be found on Github under the name @keithing.
